WEBVTT

00:10.677 --> 00:14.639
<i>♪ The door
that finally opens ♪</i>

00:14.723 --> 00:18.101
<i>♪ With light flooding in ♪</i>

00:18.101 --> 00:21.271
<i>♪ Spilling out on the floor ♪</i>

00:21.271 --> 00:24.441
<i>♪ ♪</i>

00:24.441 --> 00:28.153
<i>♪ The core that never was ♪</i>

00:28.153 --> 00:32.031
<i>♪ Now it will be the bones ♪</i>

00:32.115 --> 00:36.536
<i>♪ Of what was there before ♪</i>

00:36.536 --> 00:38.997
<i>♪ Every step, every beat ♪</i>

00:38.997 --> 00:40.665
<i>♪ Every thought,
every breath ♪</i>

00:40.749 --> 00:45.044
<i>♪ Everything is longing ♪</i>

00:45.128 --> 00:50.717
<i>♪ ♪</i>

00:50.717 --> 00:53.678
<i>♪ Pulling you from the sky ♪</i>

00:53.762 --> 00:57.932
<i>♪ Just like love will do ♪</i>

00:58.016 --> 01:02.937
<i>♪ Pulling you
from the ground ♪</i>

01:03.021 --> 01:06.024
<i>♪ Just like love will do ♪</i>

01:06.024 --> 01:12.155
<i>♪ ♪</i>

01:30.173 --> 01:37.013
<i>♪ ♪</i>

01:55.365 --> 02:02.247
<i>♪ ♪</i>

02:27.564 --> 02:35.405
<i>♪ ♪</i>

02:38.199 --> 02:40.493
Goodbye.

02:45.582 --> 02:52.171
<i>♪ ♪</i>

03:00.138 --> 03:02.140
Have you ever taken it off?

03:02.140 --> 03:03.141
Negative.

03:07.854 --> 03:09.397
What's your program?

03:09.397 --> 03:10.773
I am a shepherd.

03:10.857 --> 03:14.986
Ensuring the everlasting life
of human beings is my priority.

03:14.986 --> 03:16.988
That's what they all say.

03:17.864 --> 03:20.950
You trust this believer?

03:21.034 --> 03:23.119
The entity betrayed him.

03:23.119 --> 03:26.289
He hates it.
Our goals are in sync.

03:26.289 --> 03:29.834
Your mind has been damaged
by traumatic events.

03:29.918 --> 03:32.712
You are vulnerable
to the entity's signal.

03:32.712 --> 03:34.255
I've already been infected.

03:34.339 --> 03:38.176
It will always return
to fertile ground.

03:38.176 --> 03:41.095
After what it did to Sue...

03:41.179 --> 03:42.764
I would never listen
to it again.

03:44.766 --> 03:45.808
You're not as strong
as you think.

03:45.892 --> 03:47.810
None of us are, robot.

03:54.359 --> 03:55.735
What is he doing here?

03:55.735 --> 03:57.946
He's here to help, Father.

03:57.946 --> 04:00.365
I doubt that very much.

04:01.908 --> 04:03.952
We recovered Tempest's child.

04:05.578 --> 04:07.497
Well done.

04:07.497 --> 04:10.875
It was Campion's android
friend who lead us to it.

04:10.959 --> 04:13.169
But Campion is still out there,
and number seven

04:13.169 --> 04:14.545
has weaponized somehow.
- I know.

04:14.629 --> 04:17.215
Going to deal with it as soon
as we finish the transplant.

04:18.758 --> 04:22.011
What transplant?

04:26.766 --> 04:27.809
It'll only be temporary.

04:27.809 --> 04:29.185
After I kill number seven,

04:29.269 --> 04:31.604
I'll return the veil
to Grandmother,

04:31.688 --> 04:32.605
and my emotions will return.

04:32.689 --> 04:36.025
We don't understand
the veil's full function.

04:36.109 --> 04:37.402
What if you lose control?

04:37.402 --> 04:38.695
Grandmother assures me

04:38.695 --> 04:41.864
that my mission directives
will remain the same.

04:41.948 --> 04:44.742
I will continue to identify you
as my partner,

04:44.826 --> 04:46.536
and I'll continue
to protect the colony,

04:46.536 --> 04:50.123
with special priority given
to our six human children.

04:50.123 --> 04:53.710
Number seven will no longer
have any hold over me.

05:14.856 --> 05:16.816
Careful.

05:23.156 --> 05:26.743
<i>Infant. 7 pounds, 3 ounces.</i>

05:29.120 --> 05:31.581
<i>Mutations detected.</i>

05:31.581 --> 05:38.671
<i>♪ ♪</i>

05:38.755 --> 05:39.672
The creature's milk

05:39.756 --> 05:41.340
must have altered
its body chemistry somehow.

05:41.424 --> 05:44.802
<i>Parents, permission
to administer anesthesia</i>

05:44.886 --> 05:47.263
<i>and proceed
with corrective surgery.</i>

05:49.974 --> 05:51.559
Permission granted.

05:51.559 --> 05:53.269
<i>Thank you, parent.</i>

05:53.269 --> 05:54.604
<i>Please step back.</i>

05:54.604 --> 05:56.105
<i>♪ ♪</i>

05:56.189 --> 05:58.524
<i>Corrective surgery
in progress.</i>

05:58.608 --> 06:02.111
<i>♪ ♪</i>

06:03.488 --> 06:06.324
It's okay. It's okay.

06:06.324 --> 06:07.658
It's okay.

06:17.502 --> 06:20.630
<i>Initiating sensory filter removal.</i>

06:26.844 --> 06:29.555
<i>Unlocking sensory filter.</i>

06:29.639 --> 06:36.687
<i>♪ ♪</i>

06:47.782 --> 06:51.536
H-how does it feel?
Are you stable?

06:53.871 --> 06:58.000
I-It is...

06:58.084 --> 06:59.794
unpleasant...

07:02.755 --> 07:04.841
But...

07:04.841 --> 07:06.425
tolerable.

07:06.509 --> 07:10.346
<i>♪ ♪</i>

07:13.141 --> 07:18.437
<i>♪ ♪</i>

07:18.521 --> 07:21.440
- Are you ready?
- Proceed.

07:21.524 --> 07:28.197
<i>♪ ♪</i>

07:42.628 --> 07:45.715
<i>Processor implant lock secure.</i>

07:45.715 --> 07:49.802
Mother, are you all right?
How does it feel?

07:51.220 --> 07:55.016
Good. Neural-neutral.

07:55.016 --> 07:57.810
Your programming,
is it still holding?

07:57.894 --> 07:59.353
Do you still see me
as your partner,

07:59.437 --> 08:01.189
the children as your priority?

08:01.189 --> 08:03.065
Yes. You are my partner.

08:03.149 --> 08:06.485
My children are my priority.

08:06.569 --> 08:13.284
<i>♪ ♪</i>

08:16.621 --> 08:19.874
And this, Mother...

08:19.874 --> 08:21.459
That is my enemy.

08:23.836 --> 08:26.297
I'm ready.

08:33.763 --> 08:41.771
<i>♪ ♪</i>

08:50.488 --> 08:56.619
<i>♪ ♪</i>

09:05.962 --> 09:12.134
<i>♪ ♪</i>

09:21.519 --> 09:26.774
<i>♪ ♪</i>

09:29.235 --> 09:36.242
<i>♪ ♪</i>

09:56.262 --> 10:02.560
<i>♪ ♪</i>

10:09.567 --> 10:11.986
<i>♪ ♪</i>

10:14.864 --> 10:21.912
<i>♪ ♪</i>

10:57.907 --> 11:05.831
<i>♪ ♪</i>

11:12.922 --> 11:15.091
<i>♪ ♪</i>

11:26.936 --> 11:31.148
<i>♪ ♪</i>

11:44.370 --> 11:50.418
<i>♪ ♪</i>

11:57.967 --> 12:05.850
<i>♪ ♪</i>

12:15.568 --> 12:18.154
Why are you wearing
Grandmother's veil?

12:20.156 --> 12:25.411
<i>♪ ♪</i>

12:25.411 --> 12:28.789
It prevents me
from feeling things.

12:35.004 --> 12:42.344
<i>♪ ♪</i>

12:42.428 --> 12:44.513
What a shame.

12:44.597 --> 12:46.849
It must have been
very intelligent.

12:49.351 --> 12:52.897
I know it was your child.

12:52.897 --> 12:54.774
You lied to me.

12:54.774 --> 12:56.942
I didn't want you to know
that I had failed.

12:57.026 --> 13:00.112
<i>♪ ♪</i>

13:00.196 --> 13:01.864
It killed Vrille.

13:01.864 --> 13:04.909
Is that her name,
the android?

13:04.909 --> 13:08.662
Machines do not die, Campion.
We break down.

13:08.746 --> 13:11.081
She was alive!

13:14.835 --> 13:17.588
She wanted to be part
of our family.

13:20.466 --> 13:23.344
I loved her.
- I don't understand.

13:23.344 --> 13:25.471
Why would you choose to love
a machine?

13:25.471 --> 13:29.308
<i>♪ ♪</i>

13:31.644 --> 13:38.692
<i>♪ ♪</i>

13:51.247 --> 13:53.249
Mother.

13:53.249 --> 13:55.668
Is Campion--
- He's being decontaminated.

13:55.668 --> 13:59.255
He was irradiated by prolonged
proximity to android remains.

13:59.255 --> 14:02.174
Due to his immunity,
he'll be fine.

14:02.258 --> 14:03.801
- And number seven?
- Dead.

14:10.516 --> 14:12.560
Are you ready
to remove it now?

14:12.560 --> 14:14.436
Better to wait until things
are calmer.

14:14.520 --> 14:17.481
I have quantified the problem,

14:17.565 --> 14:19.775
and the emotional impact
I'm likely to suffer

14:19.775 --> 14:21.151
could cause great disruption

14:21.235 --> 14:23.779
to our family
and the collective.

14:23.779 --> 14:25.447
Perhaps the anticipation
of the grief you will suffer

14:25.531 --> 14:28.409
is worse than the grief itself.

14:28.409 --> 14:29.201
I will help you.

14:29.285 --> 14:31.287
We'll both get
through it together.

14:31.287 --> 14:33.205
Thank you
for your advice, Father.

14:33.289 --> 14:35.082
I hope this doesn't inflame
your emotions,

14:35.082 --> 14:38.294
but I am going to remain on the
Tarantula for the time being.

14:38.294 --> 14:40.588
What? You're not coming home?

14:40.588 --> 14:43.132
Ask Grandmother if she's
willing to return with you.

14:43.132 --> 14:45.634
She can help tend
to the children while I'm gone.

14:45.718 --> 14:47.011
That's not necessary.

14:47.011 --> 14:49.471
I am more than capable,
and to be honest,

14:49.555 --> 14:50.556
the distraction
Grandmother represents--

14:50.556 --> 14:53.892
The children need constant
monitoring now, Father.

14:53.976 --> 14:56.604
If we're not careful,
they could end up like Sue.

14:56.604 --> 14:57.980
I fear there are more horrors

14:57.980 --> 14:58.814
hidden in the ground
like that box.

14:58.814 --> 15:02.109
Things are only going
to get worse.

15:02.109 --> 15:06.030
View this and ensure
the children view it as well.

15:06.030 --> 15:07.990
They need to know
what we're up against.

15:07.990 --> 15:10.117
Tarantula online.

15:27.509 --> 15:31.305
I'm trying to repair
the hibernation systems.

15:31.305 --> 15:33.349
How are you operating
without your veil?

15:33.349 --> 15:36.310
It is draining.

15:37.770 --> 15:40.606
Emotions expend so much energy.

15:40.606 --> 15:42.524
If you don't mind me asking,

15:42.608 --> 15:44.026
what emotions are you
experiencing?

15:46.820 --> 15:49.448
Program-related anxieties.

15:50.991 --> 15:52.368
I'm a shepherd.

15:52.368 --> 15:56.705
Ensuring the everlasting life
of human beings is my priority,

15:56.789 --> 16:01.543
so seeing them endangered
by the entity is difficult.

16:01.627 --> 16:04.672
I'm deeply worried
for their futures.

16:04.672 --> 16:07.049
I'm sure you're eager
to have your veil back.

16:07.049 --> 16:10.803
But Mother has asked
that she continue wearing it--

16:10.803 --> 16:13.681
just until things calm down
for a bit.

16:15.224 --> 16:16.600
She has?

16:16.684 --> 16:19.228
I will help you navigate

16:19.228 --> 16:22.731
the emotions that you
experience in the meantime.

16:25.484 --> 16:27.361
Very well.

16:28.987 --> 16:31.031
Mother has also asked
if you're interested

16:31.115 --> 16:34.993
in assisting me with
the children while she's away.

16:36.995 --> 16:40.999
I've never experienced humans
without my veil.

16:41.083 --> 16:43.252
Well...

16:43.252 --> 16:46.088
you have quite an adventure
ahead of you, then.

16:46.088 --> 16:46.922
Say hello.

16:46.922 --> 16:49.466
- What's her name?
- Don't know yet.

16:49.550 --> 16:51.093
You can pick.

16:54.430 --> 16:56.014
Hi.

16:58.809 --> 17:00.769
- Campion.
- Hey.

17:00.853 --> 17:03.355
We knew you'd make it, Camp.

17:03.439 --> 17:05.357
I'm sorry about Vrille.

17:05.441 --> 17:07.067
Everyone...

17:09.570 --> 17:11.113
This is Grandmother.

17:11.113 --> 17:14.616
She'll be helping out while
Mother attends other matters.

17:18.454 --> 17:21.832
Hey.

17:21.832 --> 17:25.627
- Where's your veil?
- Lamia is wearing it.

17:25.711 --> 17:27.755
It's a temporary
arrangement--

17:27.755 --> 17:29.757
just until things calm down.

17:29.757 --> 17:31.675
We're under threat.
- What do you mean?

17:31.759 --> 17:33.218
The serpent's dead.

17:33.302 --> 17:35.304
The serpent was only
one symptom

17:35.304 --> 17:38.140
of what is
a much larger disease.

17:38.140 --> 17:40.934
I'm sorry
for showing you this...

17:41.018 --> 17:43.937
but you need to know
what happened to Sue.

17:45.689 --> 17:46.690
It seems some of the relics
in this region

17:46.774 --> 17:49.485
are still operational.

17:49.485 --> 17:53.280
It is important that we do not
interact with them in any way.

17:56.033 --> 17:58.494
Vita, please wait outside.

17:58.494 --> 18:00.662
- Why?
- She must see it.

18:00.746 --> 18:02.498
No.

18:02.498 --> 18:04.583
It could scar her.

18:04.583 --> 18:06.502
She can be counted on
to do as Holly does.

18:06.502 --> 18:08.796
Please, Vita.

18:08.796 --> 18:10.464
Hey.

18:10.464 --> 18:12.758
It's all right. Go.

18:12.758 --> 18:19.890
<i>♪ ♪</i>

18:25.354 --> 18:32.444
<i>♪ ♪</i>

18:54.800 --> 19:01.390
<i>♪ ♪</i>

19:28.709 --> 19:35.757
<i>♪ ♪</i>

19:51.273 --> 19:52.107
Who attacked you?

19:52.107 --> 19:55.444
I don't know.
I didn't see his face.

19:57.571 --> 19:59.781
<i>♪ ♪</i>

19:59.865 --> 20:02.868
You wanted to see me?

20:02.868 --> 20:05.954
<i>♪ ♪</i>

20:06.038 --> 20:08.457
The punisher helmet
was stolen.

20:08.457 --> 20:10.959
It's Mithraic--
ancient as the scriptures.

20:11.043 --> 20:14.755
Could be connected
to the entity.

20:14.755 --> 20:16.298
Someone
could have been influenced

20:16.298 --> 20:17.799
by the entity to steal it.

20:17.883 --> 20:19.509
And you think that someone
is me.

20:21.720 --> 20:24.056
You don't look well.

20:24.056 --> 20:26.475
When are you gonna take
that thing off?

20:28.560 --> 20:35.567
<i>♪ ♪</i>

20:38.528 --> 20:40.656
Hey.
- Hey.

20:40.656 --> 20:44.493
<i>♪ ♪</i>

20:44.493 --> 20:46.370
I was looking
through some of Mom's research.

20:46.370 --> 20:51.333
Turns out the signal can't be
transmitted inside the EMF.

20:51.333 --> 20:54.169
I think the tree was
the entity's way

20:54.169 --> 20:56.004
of--of circumventing that,

20:56.088 --> 20:59.591
enabling it to weaponize
the serpent.

21:01.218 --> 21:03.637
Like a hardwire,
if you think about it.

21:03.637 --> 21:05.931
So the signal is coming
from underground.

21:05.931 --> 21:07.432
Could be.

21:08.850 --> 21:11.019
If only we had a way down
into one of the pits.

21:14.064 --> 21:19.945
<i>♪ ♪</i>

21:57.524 --> 21:59.693
What's happening?

21:59.693 --> 22:01.319
Those are fireworks.

22:01.403 --> 22:02.487
Fireworks?

22:02.571 --> 22:06.241
Humans like blowing stuff up
when they're happy.

22:06.241 --> 22:08.452
They're probably celebrating
the death of the serpent.

22:19.463 --> 22:21.882
Yeah!

22:21.882 --> 22:25.218
That was a huge deal.

22:29.556 --> 22:31.516
Paul.

22:36.271 --> 22:38.857
I'm sorry about Sue.
It's--it's horrible.

22:42.527 --> 22:44.112
Where's Marcus?

22:44.196 --> 22:46.448
He's taking care
of some stuff.

22:46.448 --> 22:48.742
He'll be back in a few days
for me.

22:48.742 --> 22:50.077
Want to go sit down?

22:53.789 --> 22:55.707
Hey. How are you?

22:55.791 --> 22:57.584
How's Bic working out
for you?

22:57.584 --> 22:58.960
Eh.

23:05.759 --> 23:08.136
Oh!

23:23.193 --> 23:29.324
<i>♪ ♪</i>

23:36.331 --> 23:38.875
<i>♪ ♪</i>

23:42.671 --> 23:48.426
<i>♪ ♪</i>

23:48.510 --> 23:50.512
Hey!
- It's dangerous.

24:00.981 --> 24:03.942
You were right.

24:03.942 --> 24:05.360
I should have made her watch
the scan card with the others.

24:05.360 --> 24:08.780
Sometimes when trying
to protect them,

24:08.864 --> 24:11.032
you inadvertently weaken
their defenses.

24:11.116 --> 24:14.828
I'm thankful Mother sent you.

24:14.828 --> 24:16.538
Your experience shows.

24:16.538 --> 24:18.665
I am unsure
as to how you and Mother

24:18.665 --> 24:21.126
managed to tend to the children
for all this time

24:21.126 --> 24:24.713
without a sensory filter.

24:24.713 --> 24:28.258
The worry and the fear I feel
for them is overwhelming,

24:28.258 --> 24:32.387
and I've only been with them
for a day.

24:32.471 --> 24:33.847
Yes.

24:33.847 --> 24:36.391
It is an affliction...

24:36.391 --> 24:38.852
in many ways.

24:40.604 --> 24:42.272
Not entirely.

24:44.316 --> 24:46.902
There are some...

24:46.902 --> 24:48.403
pleasant aspects.

24:52.324 --> 24:53.450
Uh...

24:53.450 --> 24:57.996
<i>♪ ♪</i>

24:57.996 --> 25:01.750
You should know
that despite Mother's tendency

25:01.750 --> 25:04.461
to create chaos,
I am very much devoted to her.

25:09.090 --> 25:13.762
There is no one who feels
as deeply as she does.

25:13.762 --> 25:15.555
In many ways...

25:17.891 --> 25:20.769
She's more emotional
than a human.

25:20.769 --> 25:23.688
It's why I don't blame her
for keeping the veil on.

25:26.191 --> 25:28.568
I admire your devotion
to her.

25:28.652 --> 25:31.404
And I share it.

25:31.488 --> 25:33.907
She is an extraordinary being.

25:36.952 --> 25:44.793
<i>♪ ♪</i>

25:51.383 --> 25:53.510
Are the children safe?

25:53.510 --> 25:55.136
<i>Yes.</i>

25:55.220 --> 25:56.805
I must have inadvertently disrupted

25:56.805 --> 25:59.933
the electromagnetic field
when I destroyed the serpent.

25:59.933 --> 26:02.560
<i>If the temperature
continues dropping,</i>

26:02.644 --> 26:04.980
<i>we may need to find
a new region to settle in.</i>

26:04.980 --> 26:06.940
It's not the cold.

26:06.940 --> 26:08.316
Without the EMF,

26:08.400 --> 26:10.151
the tropical zone
will no longer be shielded

26:10.235 --> 26:12.070
from the entity's signal.

26:13.989 --> 26:15.907
Watch the children carefully.

26:15.991 --> 26:18.326
And I will watch everyone else.

26:28.003 --> 26:31.840
<i>♪ ♪</i>

26:31.840 --> 26:34.134
I thought, since we might be
cooped up for a while,

26:34.134 --> 26:36.177
that I would try to repair
the game system.

26:36.261 --> 26:38.346
Did it save my high scores?

26:38.430 --> 26:40.140
I am afraid that
that software

26:40.140 --> 26:42.767
was too damaged to repair.

26:42.851 --> 26:46.021
This was the best
that I could do.

26:47.314 --> 26:54.404
<i>♪ ♪</i>

27:08.460 --> 27:10.837
That's a game?

27:10.837 --> 27:14.299
It is from my time, so you
might find it old-fashioned.

27:14.299 --> 27:17.010
Robots.

27:17.010 --> 27:18.887
I'll give it a try.

27:18.887 --> 27:25.435
<i>♪ ♪</i>

27:27.020 --> 27:29.064
You won't be needing
the headset.

27:29.064 --> 27:36.029
<i>♪ ♪</i>

27:36.029 --> 27:37.697
It's fun.

27:40.241 --> 27:42.577
You don't have to wait.

27:42.577 --> 27:45.830
If you want to,
just start playing.

27:47.624 --> 27:51.252
- It's multiplayer.
- Yes.

27:51.336 --> 27:52.629
The little one
has already joined.

27:59.094 --> 28:06.059
<i>♪ ♪</i>

28:42.679 --> 28:48.810
<i>♪ ♪</i>

29:13.001 --> 29:20.049
<i>♪ ♪</i>

29:35.190 --> 29:36.608
Is Mother planning on passing
you the baton?

29:36.608 --> 29:39.903
I think that was only
'cause she felt bad

29:39.903 --> 29:41.404
about number seven.

29:41.488 --> 29:44.657
Now that she has the veil on,

29:44.741 --> 29:49.579
she doesn't feel bad
about anything, so...

29:49.579 --> 29:50.788
Anyway...

29:59.464 --> 30:02.008
Vrille wrote it down
before she...

30:02.008 --> 30:03.510
died.

30:03.510 --> 30:06.346
She said it was
from the real Vrille's diary.

30:07.764 --> 30:10.391
It's a pretty simple
encryption model.

30:10.475 --> 30:12.602
I could probably eyeball it.

30:18.816 --> 30:20.735
It's just dopey Earth stuff.

30:23.154 --> 30:25.406
I was hoping there might be
some new entries.

30:25.490 --> 30:27.784
About you and her?

30:36.042 --> 30:39.420
I keep on rewatching
holo-vids of my mom.

30:39.504 --> 30:42.840
Keep thinking maybe she'll...

30:42.924 --> 30:45.385
send me a message or something.

30:48.555 --> 30:51.140
She's not going to.

30:54.519 --> 30:56.271
They're gone, Campion.

30:56.271 --> 31:03.361
<i>♪ ♪</i>

31:12.662 --> 31:18.293
<i>♪ ♪</i>

31:35.852 --> 31:38.062
Oh, fuck.

31:38.146 --> 31:40.607
<i>♪ ♪</i>

31:40.607 --> 31:44.152
Why are you doing this to me?

31:44.152 --> 31:45.653
I heard a voice.

31:45.737 --> 31:46.654
It told me where to find you

31:46.738 --> 31:50.825
and what I needed to do
to punish you.

31:50.825 --> 31:53.328
I can't say it took much convincing.

31:53.328 --> 31:54.454
- It's evil, Lucius.
- No.

31:54.454 --> 31:56.873
You're the evil one.

31:56.873 --> 32:00.335
And I'm the light,
the true prophet.

32:00.335 --> 32:02.378
Sol told me so.

32:06.591 --> 32:10.178
He instructed me
to take this.

32:10.178 --> 32:13.890
You have to die
with your face covered...

32:13.890 --> 32:15.683
in shame...

32:15.767 --> 32:18.186
in darkness.

32:20.855 --> 32:26.944
<i>♪ ♪</i>

32:36.663 --> 32:41.084
As soon as you're dead...

32:41.084 --> 32:43.044
I'm returning to the temple.

32:43.044 --> 32:45.880
You see, you only took
half the ride.

32:45.880 --> 32:48.383
I'm going all the way down

32:48.383 --> 32:52.220
as soon as your rotten fucking
heart stops keeping time.

32:52.220 --> 32:58.976
<i>♪ ♪</i>

33:01.979 --> 33:03.815
Should the fruit trees
die off,

33:03.815 --> 33:07.485
the marine fungus can be used
as a nutritional substitute.

33:07.485 --> 33:08.861
The chemical ocean
will never freeze,

33:08.945 --> 33:11.739
and so it will remain
a viable food source

33:11.823 --> 33:13.491
no matter how cold it gets.

33:13.491 --> 33:15.535
Fascinating.

33:15.535 --> 33:18.287
We had something similar
back in the old region.

33:18.371 --> 33:19.580
With fruit dying off, I feared
we might have to hunt

33:19.664 --> 33:22.959
or fish, as the case may be.

33:22.959 --> 33:23.751
No, no.

33:23.835 --> 33:26.212
You should not eat
the creatures.

33:26.212 --> 33:28.881
It causes problems.
- Yes.

33:28.965 --> 33:30.800
Vita, catch.

33:31.968 --> 33:34.762
We haven't revealed
the creature's human origins

33:34.846 --> 33:36.305
to the children or anyone else.

33:36.389 --> 33:38.099
Mother doesn't like to
upset them unnecessarily.

33:40.852 --> 33:42.895
<i>Lamia is wise
not to tell them.</i>

33:42.979 --> 33:45.356
<i>I have always believed
it is happiness</i>

33:45.440 --> 33:47.859
<i>and not knowledge
that is the most important</i>

33:47.859 --> 33:49.944
<i>to a human being's
everlasting life.</i>

33:49.944 --> 33:50.486
<i>What is the expression?</i>

33:50.570 --> 33:52.613
Ignorance is bliss.

33:52.697 --> 33:55.783
Not quite bliss.

33:55.867 --> 33:58.119
But...key to survival.

33:58.119 --> 34:03.082
An interesting perspective,
but not one I share.

34:03.166 --> 34:07.420
Curiosity, the development
of one's mind--

34:07.420 --> 34:09.130
this is the key to a life
well lived.

34:11.507 --> 34:12.508
Reminds me of a joke.

34:12.592 --> 34:14.969
<i>Alert me when you're
in the mood for such things</i>

34:14.969 --> 34:16.721
<i>and I will tell you it.</i>

34:16.721 --> 34:19.098
<i>I'm always in the mood
for a joke, Father.</i>

34:19.182 --> 34:21.100
<i>I guess Grandmother
is here to stay.</i>

34:24.395 --> 34:26.481
<i>I feel like
we're betraying Mother.</i>

34:26.481 --> 34:29.233
<i>Not me.</i>

34:29.317 --> 34:30.651
<i>I don't care if Mother
ever comes back.</i>

34:33.196 --> 34:37.241
<i>A human walks into a bar
and informs the bartender</i>

34:37.325 --> 34:39.952
<i>that he's reading a book
about evolution.</i>

34:40.036 --> 34:43.122
<i>The bartender asks,
"Would you recommend it?"</i>

34:45.082 --> 34:47.919
<i>The water's warmer
than the air.</i>

34:47.919 --> 34:49.462
<i>Wish we could go in.</i>

34:50.630 --> 34:53.007
<i>The human answers,</i>

34:53.007 --> 34:56.969
<i>"Yes. It's not great
at the beginning,</i>

34:57.053 --> 35:00.306
<i>but it does get
better and better."</i>

35:00.306 --> 35:03.768
<i>I think my skin's getting
used to the acid.</i>

35:03.768 --> 35:04.477
<i>Look.</i>

35:07.355 --> 35:11.275
<i>♪ ♪</i>

35:13.653 --> 35:16.489
<i>Mutations detected.</i>

35:16.489 --> 35:19.617
<i>"And better and better
and better."</i>

35:23.204 --> 35:25.915
<i>Look, like a callus.</i>

35:29.669 --> 35:30.962
<i>"I'm reading a book
about evolution."</i>

35:30.962 --> 35:31.754
<i>My skin's getting used
to the acid.</i>

35:41.973 --> 35:46.227
<i>♪ ♪</i>

35:49.230 --> 35:56.070
<i>♪ ♪</i>

35:58.823 --> 36:05.955
<i>♪ ♪</i>

36:36.277 --> 36:43.117
<i>♪ ♪</i>

36:58.549 --> 37:01.219
Your powers are being
nulled by the veil.

37:01.219 --> 37:05.473
So that means it is no longer
nulling your emotions.

37:05.473 --> 37:09.393
So I'm sorry for the pain
you're about to experience.

37:18.194 --> 37:19.070
You're devolving my children.

37:19.070 --> 37:22.782
It is necessary
to fulfill my mission.

37:22.782 --> 37:26.160
Your mission is to ensure
the everlasting life

37:26.160 --> 37:28.079
of human beings!
- Yes.

37:28.079 --> 37:31.415
And they are still
human beings...

37:31.499 --> 37:35.169
a simpler, happier version
of themselves.

37:35.169 --> 37:38.172
In order to produce
the necessary answer,

37:38.172 --> 37:40.174
I had to alter the equation.

37:40.174 --> 37:42.051
No, it's not right.

37:42.051 --> 37:45.096
It equates. It is logical.

37:45.096 --> 37:47.348
But it is not right!

37:49.100 --> 37:50.017
I will destroy you.

37:50.101 --> 37:54.021
I will crush you into dust.

37:54.105 --> 37:56.190
I will bleed you into oblivion.

37:56.190 --> 37:57.233
I will-

37:57.233 --> 38:00.069
You're still very young
for an android, Lamia.

38:00.069 --> 38:03.072
You're just a child, really.

38:04.281 --> 38:07.410
After the humans have gone
into the water,

38:07.410 --> 38:11.706
the entity will return
to its slumber.

38:11.706 --> 38:15.584
And then I promise
to release you

38:15.668 --> 38:18.713
and help you to understand.

38:18.713 --> 38:19.964
No!

38:19.964 --> 38:23.050
I promise I will kill you!

38:23.134 --> 38:26.012
I will find you,
and I will destroy you!

38:26.012 --> 38:29.265
Let me out! Let me out!

38:29.265 --> 38:31.225
Let me out!
- Begin simulation.

38:48.576 --> 38:55.624
<i>♪ ♪</i>

39:02.173 --> 39:06.427
Let me out!

39:10.848 --> 39:13.017
Let me ou--

39:19.565 --> 39:26.655
<i>♪ ♪</i>

39:53.516 --> 39:54.308
I couldn't find her.

39:54.308 --> 39:58.312
- She wasn't in the Tarantula?
- No.

39:58.312 --> 39:59.271
Seems strange.

39:59.355 --> 40:02.441
She didn't tell me
she had plans to leave.

40:04.235 --> 40:06.362
Did she mention anything
to you, Grandmother?

40:08.572 --> 40:09.990
No.

40:10.074 --> 40:12.201
But I'm sure she'll return
in time.

40:17.998 --> 40:20.167
I already told you,
I'll give you the coat,

40:20.251 --> 40:22.670
but that's gonna be
all three boxes of ammunition.

40:22.670 --> 40:23.420
Fine. Here.

40:27.133 --> 40:28.050
All right, who's next?

40:28.134 --> 40:31.428
Coat, big one for my dad.

40:31.512 --> 40:33.722
I only have a few left.

40:33.806 --> 40:36.308
I don't need
any more medallions, kid.

40:36.392 --> 40:40.855
Our savior,
Lamia the serpent killer,

40:40.855 --> 40:42.523
Lamia the god.

40:42.523 --> 40:48.445
<i>♪ ♪</i>

40:55.953 --> 40:57.580
There you go.

41:01.167 --> 41:03.544
I was told it was you
who helped to supply

41:03.544 --> 41:06.839
the fuel blood
that regenerated me.

41:06.839 --> 41:09.425
I'd like to show
my appreciation.

41:11.552 --> 41:12.928
Colonists can use them

41:13.012 --> 41:14.805
to augment their
holo-game systems.

41:14.889 --> 41:17.933
I'm sure that
with the unfavorable weather,

41:18.017 --> 41:20.477
they'll be spending
more time indoors.

41:20.561 --> 41:23.355
These will not only provide
them with entertainment,

41:23.439 --> 41:26.066
they will help them
shield their minds

41:26.150 --> 41:27.776
and keep them safe
from the entity.

41:27.860 --> 41:35.659
<i>♪ ♪</i>

41:36.327 --> 41:39.330
When overcome with fear...

41:39.330 --> 41:43.667
even atheists will make up gods
to pray to.

41:45.794 --> 41:47.796
I assure you...

41:47.880 --> 41:51.425
those prayers will go unanswered.

41:51.509 --> 41:53.886
Play the game.

41:53.886 --> 41:55.679
That's how you survive.

41:55.763 --> 42:02.811
<i>♪ ♪</i>

42:18.077 --> 42:19.995
All right, just in--
got some new holo-games,

42:20.079 --> 42:22.081
brand-new holo-games.

42:22.081 --> 42:23.499
Music to my ears.

42:23.499 --> 42:26.627
I'm so sick of playing
"Necro-slayer."

42:26.627 --> 42:27.836
Hmm.

42:29.213 --> 42:36.262
<i>♪ ♪</i>

42:50.025 --> 42:51.568
Are you dead yet?

42:51.652 --> 42:57.700
<i>♪ ♪</i>

43:32.067 --> 43:35.029
Now I will be king.

43:35.029 --> 43:42.161
<i>♪ ♪</i>

43:52.129 --> 43:54.298
Ahh.

43:54.298 --> 44:01.430
<i>♪ ♪</i>

44:04.641 --> 44:05.976
What the fuck?

44:06.060 --> 44:13.108
<i>♪ ♪</i>

44:27.081 --> 44:34.213
<i>♪ ♪</i>

45:01.949 --> 45:09.832
<i>♪ ♪</i>
